CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 2, 1955, pg. 3 reads: "New Safety Department Head - David Olbum, public safety director for Pittsburgh, is working towards the efficient coordination of the various bureaus on the department. "No longer will the bureaus act independently," says Mr. Olbum. He is also available to the public. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of David Olbum wearing striped suit and diagonally striped necktie, standing at window with hands in pockets in office interior
